---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { SITE_TITLE, SITE_DESCRIPTION } from '../consts';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title={SITE_TITLE} description={SITE_DESCRIPTION} />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<h1>Daniel Kiptoon</h1>
			<p>
				I build reliable software systems for products that need to scale, stay observable, and
				keep moving in production.
			</p>
			<p>
				I am a software engineer with 6+ years of experience across fintech, analytics, developer
				tooling, and cloud-native systems. My recent work has focused on Kubernetes discovery,
				distributed backends, and performance-sensitive services, and I recently completed an MSc in
				Artificial Intelligence with distinction.
			</p>
			<p>
				This site is where I share notes from the systems I build, the operational lessons that
				stick, and the engineering trade-offs behind backend and platform work.
			</p>
			<h2>What I work on</h2>
			<ul>
				<li>Kubernetes operators, discovery, and cluster-scale performance</li>
				<li>Backend services in Go, Python, and .NET</li>
				<li>Distributed systems, messaging pipelines, and API design</li>
				<li>Applied AI and ML systems with a strong engineering foundation</li>
			</ul>
			<p>
				Start with the <a href="/blog">blog</a> for technical writing, or visit the
				<a href="/about">about page</a> for a fuller background on my work.
			</p>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
